            <title><![CDATA[Switch 2 Pro Controller's Charging Time Is Half That Of The Original Device, Nintendo Says]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/switch-2-pro-controllers-charging-time-is-half-that-of-the-original-device-nintendo-says/1100-6531004/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
